@startuml seq-timeline-feed
participant Browser
participant "Posts Service" as PS
participant "Users Service" as US
participant "Posts DB" as DB

Browser -> PS: GET /feed [Bearer JWT]
PS -> US: GET /users/{user_id}/followees
US --> PS: 200 OK {followee_ids[]}
PS -> DB: SELECT posts WHERE author_id IN (followees)\nORDER BY created_at DESC LIMIT 20
DB --> PS: posts[]
PS -> US: GET /users/{id} (batch enrich authors)
US --> PS: 200 OK {profiles[]}
PS --> Browser: 200 OK {posts[]}
@enduml
